      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; experimental sample sizes from FDA interlaboratory study are documented.",
      "rationale": "The FDA interlaboratory dataset includes results from six independent laboratories providing statistical coverage. Formal sample-size adequacy analysis is not required at MRL 2; the multi-laboratory provenance provides inherent robustness."
