      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; qualitative mapping between experimental and simulation input parameters documented.",
      "rationale": "A parameter mapping table was prepared documenting the correspondence between experimental measurement conditions and CFD boundary conditions. Formal equivalency scoring is deferred to MRL 3 upgrade pathway."
